/*
 * Integrated Sound Level Meter and Dosimeter
 *  
 * Calibrate and change caloffset (suggested -11db as baseline)
 * Wiring summary:
 *   Microphone (INMP441)  : SD=32, WS=25, SCK=26, VDD=3.3V, L/R=GND
 *   Display   (ILI9341)   : CS=22, DC=4, RST=5, MOSI=23, SCK=18, MISO=19
 *   Reset button          : GPIO 15 → GND
 *   Mode button           : GPIO 13 → GND
 *
 * WiFi: connect to "SoundDosimeter" / "12345678" then open http://192.168.4.1
 */

